.NET Framework 3.5.name: VRTK_InteractHaptics
.NET Framework 3.5.summary: The Interact Haptics script is attached on the same GameObject as an Interactable Object script and provides controller haptics on touch, grab and use of the object.

methods.name: HapticsOnGrab(uint controllerIndex)
methods.summary: The HapticsOnGrab method triggers the haptic feedback on the given controller for the settings associated with grab.

params.value: The controller index to activate the haptic feedback on.

methods.name: HapticsOnGrab(VRTK_ControllerReference controllerReference)
methods.summary: The HapticsOnGrab method triggers the haptic feedback on the given controller for the settings associated with grab.

params.value: The reference to the controller to activate the haptic feedback on.
